Save to `{{ "{" }}workspace{{ "}" }}/one-on-ones/{{ "{" }}person-slug{{ "}" }}/{{ "{" }}YYYY-MM-DD{{ "}" }}.md` (one folder per person, so history accrues) and surface inline:

